    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until warmed through and starting to brown</p><p>Once starting to brown, add your <strong>red chilli relish </strong>to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>sweet chilli meat-free chick'n</strong></p>",
