    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice each <strong>warmed baguette</strong> in half (without cutting all the way through) and open it out like a book</p><p>Spread over the <strong>mushroom pâté </strong>and top with the<strong> sweet chilli meat-free chick'n</strong>,<strong> carrot ribbons</strong>, <strong>cucumber slices </strong>and<strong> mint & coriander leaves </strong>– this is your <strong>sweet chilli meat-free chick'n & mushroom báhn mì</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>quick-pickled salad </strong>and<strong> sriracha mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
